<h1 style="color: #dc3545;">I-9 Verification Issue</h1>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  There is an issue with the I-9 employment eligibility verification for
  <strong><%= @candidate.full_name %></strong> for the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position.
</p>

<h2>Status</h2>

<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #dc3545; padding: 10px; background-color: #f8d7da; border-radius: 4px;">
  <strong>Verification Failed</strong>
</p>

<h2>Candidate Details</h2>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Employee:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @candidate.full_name %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Position:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @job.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Expected Start Date:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @i9_verification&.employee_start_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>Required Actions</h2>

<p>
  Please review the I-9 verification details and take appropriate action.
  This may include:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Contacting the employee to request additional documentation</li>
  <li>Reviewing E-Verify results if applicable</li>
  <li>Consulting with legal counsel if needed</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
  <strong>Important:</strong> Do not make employment decisions based solely on national origin
  or citizenship status. Follow USCIS guidelines and consult legal counsel if needed.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  <%= PlatformBrand.name %> System
</p>
